nodes.text: Looca B'Nash was a male Duros who lived on the moon Pinett during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

A Force-sensitive Duros living during the reign of the Galactic Empire, Looca B'Nash lived on the moon Pinett where he made his living as a lieutenant of the Human smuggler Jaeth. After the Corsignis Property Alliance and the Jon-Tow Economic Development Group blockaded Pinett as a result of a trade dispute, the Pinett Freedom Force, a local protest movement, attempted to prevent Corsignis and Jon-Tow starships from landing on the moon. However, a number of port workers became disgruntled as a result of the Freedom Force's actions, and under the leadership of Jaeth and B'Nash, the port workers began to cause trouble for the Freedom Force.
